<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.3">
<l>koṇṭāṭṭuṅ kulampuṉaivun tamaruṟṟār viḻunitiyum</l>
<l>vaṇṭārpūṅ kuḻalāḷu maṉaiyoḻiya vuyirmāytal</l>
<l>kaṇṭāṟṟē ṉulakiyaṟkai kaṭalvaṇṇā vaṭiyēṉaip</l>
<l>paṇṭēpōl karutātu ṉaṭikkēkūyap paṇikoḷḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I can’t bear seeing life vanish, while appreciation, the beauty of the famly,</l>
<l>the excellent treasure of those who have their people and those with curls in which bees hum</l>
<l>stay behind in the house. [It is] the nature of the world, you of ocean colour. Like before</l>
<l>without thinking take me, [your] servant, to your feet as a servant to be called.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
